---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About Us — Resurgence Builds" description="Learn more about Resurgence Builds, a passion project dedicated to The Division Resurgence.">
  <div class="container section content-width">
    <h1 class="heading-accent">About Us</h1>
    
    <div class="prose">
      <p>Welcome to <strong>Resurgence Builds</strong>. We're a small crew of Division Resurgence players who got tired of Googling "best Vanguard build" and getting the same recycled garbage from sites that have never loaded into a Dark Zone.</p>
      
      <h2>Why We Built This</h2>
      <p>Every other "build guide" site reads like it was written by someone who watched one YouTube video and called it research. We actually play the game. We test the builds. We argue about the math in Discord until 2am. Then we write it down so you don't have to.</p>
      
      <h2>What You Get</h2>
      <p>Builds that work. Guides that explain the why, not just the what. Patch notes that tell you if your build just got murdered by Ubisoft. No paywalls, no gated content, no "subscribe for the REAL build." Everything is here. We run a few ads to keep the lights on because hosting costs money and we refuse to sell you a battle pass for a website.</p>
      
      <h2>Get Involved</h2>
      <p>Have a build that's shredding the Dark Zone? Found a typo? Just want to tell us our tier list is wrong? We're always looking for feedback. Hit us up on Discord or drop a comment. We read everything. We respond to most of it. We fix the stuff that's actually wrong.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
